ID.name: ID
ID.description: The `ID` scalar type represents a unique identifier, often used to refetch an object or as key for a cache. The ID type appears in a JSON response as a String; however, it is not intended to be human-readable. When expected as an input type, any string (such as `"4"`) or integer (such as `4`) input value will be accepted as an ID.

Int.name: Int
Int.description: The `Int` scalar type represents non-fractional signed whole numeric values. Int can represent values between -(2^31) and 2^31 - 1.

Float.name: Float
Float.description: The `Float` scalar type represents signed double-precision fractional values as specified by [IEEE 754](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IEEE_floating_point).

String.name: String
String.description: The `String` scalar type represents textual data, represented as UTF-8 character sequences. The String type is most often used by GraphQL to represent free-form human-readable text.

skip.name: skip
skip.description: Directs the executor to skip this field or fragment when the `if` argument is true.

oneOf.name: oneOf
oneOf.description: Indicates exactly one field must be supplied and this field must not be `null`.

include.name: include
include.description: Directs the executor to include this field or fragment only when the `if` argument is true.

args.name: reason
args.description: Explains why this element was deprecated, usually also including a suggestion for how to access supported similar data. Formatted using the Markdown syntax, as specified by [CommonMark](https://commonmark.org/).

deprecated.name: deprecated
deprecated.description: Marks an element of a GraphQL schema as no longer supported.

args.name: url
args.description: The URL that specifies the behavior of this scalar.

specifiedBy.name: specifiedBy
specifiedBy.description: Exposes a URL that specifies the behavior of this scalar.

query_list.query:
query Query ($filter: CountryFilterInput){
  countries (filter: $filter){
    awsRegion
    capital
    code
    currencies
    currency
    emoji
    emojiU
    name
    native
    phone
    phones
  }
}

query_list.name: 变量（filter）
query_list.query:
query Query {
  countries(filter: {code: {eq: "AE"}}) {
    awsRegion
    capital
    code
    currencies
    currency
    emoji
    emojiU
    name
    native
    phone
    phones
  }
}
